  <bodyText><![CDATA[<h2>All Aboard: FREE First Class Rail Upgrade on Your Transfer to Swiss Resort | Offer ends 2nd October 2023</h2>
<p>Hop aboard our Swiss rail transfer offer and enjoy a complimentary upgrade to first class on your transfer rail journey. Sit back, soak up the views and let us treat you to an unforgettable journey.</p>
<p><img style="width: 100%; height: auto;" src="/media/13098320/swiss-rail-838x450.jpg?width=500&amp;height=268.49642004773267" alt="swiss rail transfer offer" data-udi="umb://media/4783ff9e9b83444c9a0276beea2e438b" /></p>
<p>Enjoy the beauty of Switzerland’s great outdoors with our exclusive Swiss rail transfer offer. You’ll be treated to a first-class upgrade as you take a remarkable journey through Switzerland’s unspoiled landscapes.</p>
<p>Switzerland is renowned for its beautiful alpine scenery, and our rail transfer offer allows you to witness its natural wonders firsthand.</p>
<p>For those planning a Switzerland multi-centre trip, we’ve got you covered too. You can experience the comfort of First Class transfers between resorts throughout your entire journey.</p>
<p>This offer is valid on all new Inghams Walking bookings for travel in 2023 and 2024. <strong><a data-udi="umb://document/67e4acb561fb4afb94500603729fb7bf" href="/{localLink:umb://document/67e4acb561fb4afb94500603729fb7bf}#Terms" title="Swiss Rail Transfer Offer" data-anchor="#Terms">Please view our full terms and conditions for more information.</a></strong> <br /><br /></p>
<p>Hurry, this offer ends 2nd October 2023. Secure your seat today and enjoy:</p>
<ul>
<li>Extra room for yourself and your luggage.</li>
<li>Relax and unwind with spacious seating, designed to provide ample leg room for your comfort throughout the entire journey.</li>
<li>Stay connected and powered up with conveniently located power sockets.</li>
<li>Variety of seating options which include 2-seat and 1-seat arrangements.</li>
<li>Dedicated quiet zones.</li>
</ul>
<p> </p>
<div><a data-udi="umb://document/02a5945a51fe4587bf5aa72b66298bea" href="/{localLink:umb://document/02a5945a51fe4587bf5aa72b66298bea}" title="Switzerland" class="c-btn">View 2023 Switzerland Holidays</a></div>
<div><a data-udi="umb://document/70f23acd5b5c42c6aca9a810dd57274d" href="/{localLink:umb://document/70f23acd5b5c42c6aca9a810dd57274d}" title="Switzerland" class="c-btn">View 2024 Switzerland Holidays</a>
<p> </p>
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<h2 style="text-align: center;"><strong>Why Book With Inghams?</strong></h2>
<h2 style="text-align: center;"><img style="width: 100%; height: auto;" src="/media/13089493/our-holidays-838x220.jpg?width=500&amp;height=131.2649164677804" alt="walking holidays europe" data-udi="umb://media/b40cf9d23b4a4012aaed9b15dfdb0eab" /></h2>
<p style="text-align: center;">✔️ With over 85 years of experience you can trust us to deliver your perfect holiday.</p>
<p style="text-align: center;">✔️ You'll have the reassurance and expert guidance of our reps when in resort.</p>
<p style="text-align: center;">✔️ <strong>New:</strong> enjoy two guided walks per week in selected resorts*.</p>
<p style="text-align: center;">✔️Flights from your choice of 15 regional airports, transfers and accommodation are included in your holiday.</p>
</div>
<p> </p>
<h2>Travel With Confidence</h2>
<p>When you book with us you can travel with confidence. We've got you covered from the moment you step out of your front door to the moment you return with incredible memories. </p>
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/fa72be9e45bc442089252c6a18a0d2ae" href="/{localLink:umb://document/fa72be9e45bc442089252c6a18a0d2ae}" title="In Safe Hands">You're in safe hands.</a></p>
<p> </p>
<p><img style="width: 100%; height: auto;" src="/media/13095389/inghams-in-safe-hands-charcoal.png?width=500&amp;height=126.45687645687646" alt="in safe hands" data-udi="umb://media/afba17a916e84fcc848acce5dda4f9c4" /></p>
<p> </p>
<p><a name="Terms"></a></p>
<p><strong>Terms and Conditions</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Free first class rail transfer upgrade is available on resort transfers in Switzerland when travelling from Geneva or Zurich airports.</li>
<li>Upgrade is applicable on all new bookings travelling between 17 July and 14 October 2023, and departures between 18 May and 12 October 2024.</li>
<li>Upgrade is applicable on multi-centre tours, where transfers between resorts are by train. The exception to this is on our Swiss Classic Tour and Glacier Express Tour, where the upgrade offer is excluded.</li>
<li>Upgrade can be used in conjunction with other offers.</li>
<li>Upgrade is available whilst stocks last, is subject to availability and can be withdrawn or amended at any time without notice.</li>
<li>Offer ends 2nd October 2023.</li>
</ul>
</div>]]></bodyText>
